{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=k|わろ}}
{{IPAfont|⟨waro<sub>2</sub>⟩}} → *{{IPAfont|/warə/}} → {{IPAchar|/waro/}}

{{inh|ja|ojp|-}}. Ancient eastern dialect. Likely a compound of {{suffix|ja|sort=わろ|我|tr1=wa|pos1=see above|ろ|tr2=ro|pos2={{etyl|ojp|-}} suffix indicating affection}}.

{{ja-pos|pronoun|わろ}}

# {{lb|ja|sort=わろ|regional|obsolete}} ''[[first person]] [[personal pronoun]]'': [[I]], [[me]], [[oneself]]
