#*: {{ux|ojp|'''和呂'''多比波 多比等於米保等 已比尓志弖 古米知夜須良牟 和加美可奈志母}}

{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=k|あれ}}
From {{suffix|ja|sort=あれ|我|tr1=a|pos1=see above|れ|tr2=re|pos2=nominalizing suffix}}

Fell into disuse in roughly the [[w:Heian period|Heian period]],<ref name="DJR"/> when it was replaced by ''ware'' (see above).

